    <briefdescription>
<para>Parameters for periodic advertising sync transfer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct defines the parameters for configuring periodic advertising sync transfers (PASTs). It includes settings for the maximum event skip, synchronization timeout, and options for sync transfer.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Used in the <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1gaa0658bd53df1d5e8e89e13330e4fd0ae" kindref="member">bt_le_per_adv_sync_transfer_subscribe</ref> function to configure sync transfer settings. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
